data.description:
Space, Privacy and Convenience.   Enjoy sitting on your rocking chair front porch.  Plenty room for a garden in the
level back yard. 3 good size bedrooms upstairs.  Primary Suite is huge- 21' x 11' with spacious double closets.
The Living room 20'x13', Formal Dining Room 11'x12' has double windows looking out to the huge
LEVEL back yard.  Eat in kitchen is 11'x12', window over the sink also looks out to the back yard.
Lot of natural light in this home.
The large, separate Laundry room 8'X7", has wood storage shelves and a work sink - perfect size.
The Pantry is a walk-in convenient to the kitchen.
Step into the Den/Bonus Room 12'x17', Real Brick fireplace, Buck stove, double windows.
Want a Large/Oversized Garage??? -  22'.10'x30'.11"-  Double Garage Doors plus a Service door to the outside.  Plenty of room for a large workshop or great storage.
This home has been cared for and loved for a number of years and now needs a new owner to enjoy
many happy years ahead!
